Intro to R

library(gplots)

UVM <- read.csv("data/UVM.csv")

Counts <- UVM[ , 4:21]

rownames(Counts) <- UVM$Gene.Name

boxplot(Counts)


Clog2 <- log2(Counts)
boxplot(Clog2)

plot(Clog2$h1, Clog2$h1.1)

heatmap.2(as.matrix(Clog2))
